DTSTAMP:20260717T013253Z
DTSTART:20260803T090000
DTEND:20260803T120000
SUMMARY:TK-3 P-3 Alignment
LOCATION:Santa Clara County Office of Education\, Ridder Park Drive\, San Jose\, CA\, USA
DESCRIPTION:The session will focus on the California Preschool through Third Grade (PK-3) Learning Progressions which map the developmental pathways of children's knowledge and skills over time. They ensure continuous\, developmentally appropriate education by linking early learning foundations to later elementary standards across five core developmental domains.\n\nThe session will be recorded\; therefore\, a waiver must be signed upon arrival and check-in.\n\nThere will be assigned seating.
END:VEVENT
